com.brawlbots.autobattler

Class Elo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brawlbots.autobattler.Elo

  • public class Elo
extends java.lang.Object
    A really simple ELO class. There is poor conservation of total ELO from double precision rounding errors.
    Author:
    Tom Ladyman
